# gradle.properties is intentionally TRACKED in this repo (was previously
# gitignored on 2026-05-09 — removed because new clones / fresh syncs
# couldn't build without it; the build.gradle reads `hermesEnabled`,
# `newArchEnabled`, `android.useAndroidX` etc. from it).
#
# IMPORTANT: any change to android/gradle.properties (Java path, JVM
# args, hermes/newArch toggles, signing config) MUST be committed so that
# every clone and every upstream-sync of this repo sees the same gradle
# settings. Do NOT add it back to .gitignore.
#
# Secret values (release-keystore passwords) belong in this file ONLY as
# placeholder TODO_* tokens for now; if real release-signing credentials
# need persistence, move them to a per-machine ~/.gradle/gradle.properties
# (which gradle merges automatically) — never put plaintext signing
# passwords in a tracked file.
